title: Arbor Snowboards FACE/OFF at Boreal
description: On April 15th, 2012 Arbor Snowboard's FACE/OFF event was held at Boreal Mountain Resort near Lake Tahoe. Some of the riders included the defending champ from last year's FACE/OFF event, Erik Leon, along with Ben Ross, Kai Wiggens, Colton Morgan, Alex Here
